# Feature Requirements

## Group Generator
- Input field for participant names (comma-separated)
- Slider/control to adjust number of groups
- Algorithm to create balanced groups
- Visual display of generated groups
- Ability to manually adjust group assignments

## Match Scorer
- Templates for different sports (Tennis, Badminton, Table Tennis, Basketball)
- Score tracking with increment/decrement controls
- Timer functionality for timed sports
- Match history recording
- Player name input fields
- Set tracking for multi-set games

## LED Scroller
- Text input for custom messages
- Color picker for text and background
- Speed adjustment slider
- Full-screen display mode
- Pre-defined templates for common sports messages
- Scrolling animation for text

## Settings
- App information section
- Feature walkthrough option
- Legal documents (License Agreement, Privacy Policy)
- Feedback submission
- Version information display
- Preferences toggles (Dark Mode, Haptic Feedback, Sound Effects, Auto-save)